data.description: Looking for a luxurious mountain retreat with breathtaking views and easy access to both East Ellijay and Jasper? Look no further than this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom property nestled in the heart of the mountains, boasting some of the most gorgeous views you'll ever lay eyes on. Upon entering this home, the open-concept living area with large windows will immediately capture your attention, providing you with a spectacular view of the mountains. A large rock fireplace creates a cozy environment for you and your guests. The gourmet kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, white cabinets, a kitchen island, pantry, and solid surface counters, with views to the family room, making it the perfect space for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The open-concept dining area is perfect for hosting dinner parties or family gatherings. This home also features a large master bedroom with large windows, allowing for plenty of natural light. The luxurious master bath includes double vanities, separate his/hers areas, a separate tub and shower, and a soaking tub perfect for relaxing after a long day. Other features of this mountain home include a laundry room and mudroom conveniently located on the main level, as well as a basement complete with a full bathroom, two bedrooms, an exercise room, a storm shelter with a custom vault door, and drive-under storage. With stunning mountain views visible from nearly every room in the house, you'll feel like you're living in a private oasis. Despite its secluded location, this property is just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment, offering the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. The property is conveniently situated between East Ellijay and Jasper, giving you a private mountain retreat with easy access to shopping. This property is the perfect blend of luxury and functionality, with every detail carefully considered to create a space that is both beautiful and practical. Whether you're seeking outdoor adventure or a peaceful retreat, this home has everything you need to relax, unwind, and recharge.
